These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, coach, doctor, mechanic
1. the mechanic is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
2. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
3. the coach is not to the left of the doctor##8
4. the coach is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Job   | doctor | coach | mechanic | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, almond-milk, juice
1. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | almond-milk | tea | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, raspberry, lemon, lime
1. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating lime##1
3. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the person eating lime##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | spinach | lime | raspberry | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, cooking, drawing, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | cooking | traveling | drawing | fishing |

 #################################

 
