.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, carrot, watermelon, radish
1. the person eating radish is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating peas is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person eating carrot##8
4. the person eating peas is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |     3     |   4   |
| Food   | radish | carrot | peas | watermelon |

